  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/5752ead5a609057a7bf60039cec70bad.webp?t=1737179835\" width=269 height=36 /></span><br>Fight your way through 66 levels. Choose one of three goals in each level:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Defend yourself until the entire map is purified<br></li><li> Destroy all enemy portals<br></li><li> Find the key and escape</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/bf23545c35c0c767720fd5aa6d7a6c5c.webp?t=1737179835\" width=263 height=45 /></span><br>Kill all ten bosses on your way to meet the devil himself. Each boss has a more or less complex level. Find out how you can beat them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/f09565ad2b916a9f8804912d7709e797.webp?t=1737179835\" width=324 height=41 /></span><br>Choose from 39 skills, organized into three main groups and three additional weapon groups to upgrade them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/2d12bb0d05cd8548f9bd17fabed91454.webp?t=1737179835\" width=380 height=44 /></span><br>Each difficulty has its own Steam leader board, see if you can break the high score and reach the top.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/5752ead5a609057a7bf60039cec70bad.webp?t=1737179835\" width=269 height=36 /></span><br>Fight your way through 66 levels. Choose one of three goals in each level:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Defend yourself until the entire map is purified<br></li><li> Destroy all enemy portals<br></li><li> Find the key and escape</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/bf23545c35c0c767720fd5aa6d7a6c5c.webp?t=1737179835\" width=263 height=45 /></span><br>Kill all ten bosses on your way to meet the devil himself. Each boss has a more or less complex level. Find out how you can beat them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/f09565ad2b916a9f8804912d7709e797.webp?t=1737179835\" width=324 height=41 /></span><br>Choose from 39 skills, organized into three main groups and three additional weapon groups to upgrade them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646740/extras/2d12bb0d05cd8548f9bd17fabed91454.webp?t=1737179835\" width=380 height=44 /></span><br>Each difficulty has its own Steam leader board, see if you can break the high score and reach the top.",
